flowchart TB
  subgraph Contract[合同上传流程（卖家）]
    direction TB
    C1[进入合同中心]
    C2[GET /contracts 查看待上传合同]
    C3[选择 PDF 文件]
    C4[POST /files<br/>purpose=CONTRACT_EVIDENCE]
    C5[POST /contracts/:contractId/upload<br/>contractFileId]
    C6[合同状态 -> WAIT_CONFIRM]

    C1 --> C2 --> C3 --> C4 --> C5 --> C6
  end

  subgraph Invoice[发票上传流程（财务/管理员）]
    direction TB
    I1[用户提交开票申请<br/>POST /orders/:orderId/invoice-requests]
    I2[状态 -> APPLYING]
    I3[财务上传电子发票 PDF<br/>POST /files purpose=INVOICE]
    I4[绑定发票到订单<br/>PUT /admin/orders/:orderId/invoice]
    I5[状态 -> ISSUED]
    I6[用户端下载<br/>GET /orders/:orderId/invoice 或 GET /invoices]

    I1 --> I2 --> I3 --> I4 --> I5 --> I6
  end

  C6 -.合同可查阅.-> I1
